after each sentence

*Mrtav* je čovek ležao u ulici. (A dead man was lying in the street.)

U njemu je bilo toliko *mrtavih* misli. (So many dead thoughts were in him.)

Tužno je bilo slušati njegov *mrtav* glas. (It was sad to hear his dead voice.)

U njegovom srcu je već dugo bilo *mrtvo*. (His heart had been dead for a long time.)

Ona je već postala *mrtva* duša. (She had already become a dead soul.)

U njenom srcu je ostala *mrtva* tišina. (Dead silence remained in her heart.)